text: Can we be done with these shitty attempts at "HORROR"? These movies are NOT scary and only a 12 year old girl would think they are. How is this horror? A couple of noises and demonic possessions? The trailers claim CHARLIE HAS HIS ROPE...then they have the nerve to put him in the same group with Freddy and Jason? THOSE were horror movies. These crappy, low budget, shaky films are not. I thought this would actually HAVE a killer in...but nope...another crappy NO SHOW ghost movie. Thanks America in particular, for making stupid, boring people rich, with stupid, low budget, anti climactic horror movies. These movies are NOT horror and if all they can muster up is one or two jump scares, then horror movies have really gotten just sad. Halloween is one of the best horror movies of all time. It makes me sick seeing people praise PARANORMAL ACTIVITY as one of the best horror movies and say how scary it was. The movie sucked and it was a cheap attempt at making money, which it did. Overhyped garbage. Damn. Child's Play was more creepy than this. Some people say how "it's scary because you CAN'T see it.." Umm...that is a lame attempt at justifying your cheap imagination and inability to write a good horror movie. We want to watch a MOVIE. Not some lame attempt at making it REAL because it ends up looking even more fake and comes off as boring. Rant over..damn!
